    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>in a bowl with a drizzle of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p>",
