    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>in a separate bowl – this is your <strong>harissa yoghurt</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, and pat it dry with kitchen paper, then roughly shred and toss in the dressing</p>",
