    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>remaining ras el hanout </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, remove the pot from the heat, then add the <strong>drained couscous</strong> and <strong>roasted vegetables </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tagine-style squash with giant couscous</strong></p>",
