      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>in a wide bowl topped with the <strong>tagine-style squash with giant couscous </strong>– this is your<strong> tagine-style salad with giant couscous</strong></p><p>Dollop over the <strong>harissa yoghurt </strong>and garnish with the<strong> chopped mint</strong>, <strong>pomegranate seeds </strong>and <strong>flaked almonds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
